<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEOPLE: L.A. COUNTY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Security Pacific National Bank has named Richard Martens executive vice 
president, heading the retail lending group. Martens previously was senior vice 
president in charge of credit administration for the retail bank. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA061389-0020 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 69474 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 13, 1989, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part 4; Page 3; Column 3; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
36 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEOPLE: L.A. COUNTY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Denise K. Gurin has been named senior vice president and head film buyer of the 
West division of AMC Film Marketing Inc. Gurin previously was vice president 
and film buyer for the West division in Los Angeles. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
