<P>
Ex-model and restaurateur Marilyn Lewis, who was once part of the Andy Warhol 
clique and is now making a documentary about the artist, believes Warhol was 
"one of the most unusual men of our times. He was terribly religious. He was a 
voyeur regarding drugs, sex and other elements of life but not a participant." 
Lewis suspects the world hasn't seen the last of Warhol. "I believe Andy is an 
afterlife person. He spent his life preparing for a reincarnation." ALEENE 
MacMINN 
