Franco, kindergartners at Santa Isabel school on Whittier Boulevard, who were 
frightened by the trembling ground. CON KEYES / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Bits 
of plaster litter floor at Board of Public Works hearing room. KEN LUBAS / Los 
Angeles Times 
